        dc:description           "Figure 46. Living snails from Bau A Japonia barbata (L. Pfeiffer, 1855) ME 8768 Gunung Kapor B Opisthophorus euryomphalus (L. Pfeiffer, 1856) ME 8779 Gunung Kapor C Opisthophorus biciliatus Mousson, 1849 ME 8754 Gunung Kapor D Opisthophorus birostris (L. Pfeiffer, 1854) ME 8755 Gunung Kapor. All not to scale." , "Figure 4. A Japonia barbata (L. Pfeiffer, 1855) ME 833 Kampung Bunga Rampai B Japonia barbata (L. Pfeiffer, 1855) ME 2141 Lobang Angin C Japonia bauensis sp. nov., ME 7231 paratype Gunung Kapor D Japonia bauensis sp. nov., MZU. MOL. 20.02 holotype Gunung Doya." ;
